# Data: processed legal text (backend/data/raw/*.txt) and source HTML
# (backend/data/raw_html/) ARE committed — they are the ingestion input and
# hard to re-fetch (vbpl.vn is behind reCAPTCHA). Regenerate the .txt from the
# HTML with scripts/html_to_legal_text.py.

# LƯU Ý: các thư mục sau CỐ Ý được commit để giữ traceability
# - docs/intake/       (bằng chứng agent đã hiểu tài liệu Nhật)
# - docs/04-decisions/ (long-term memory cho clarify)
# - specs/             (spec.md, plan.md, tasks.md do Spec Kit sinh)
